##Foxconn most difficult to most expensive "back to work season" : North of Guangzhou and Shenzhen some agents to get back fees as high as 17,000 yuan

Micro Signal China Business Journal

Function introduction, grow in step with Chinese enterprises, talk with business leaders, spread business ideals, serve business people, "China Business News" control of the absolute voice of Chinese business.

The following article is from the Isobath, by Jiang Li Chao Cheng Chen Hao

In depth report

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Jiang Zheng, Li Chao, Cheng Wei, Chen Jialan, Hao Jiagqi, Zhengzhou, Yantai, Chongqing and Taiyuan contributed reporting

Cui Yongqiang (not his real name) , who has worked at Foxconn for more than 10 years, did not end this year's Lunar New Year holiday until Feb. 27. Because of the new crown pneumonia epidemic, according to the company requirements, his home area, has not been included in the order of return to work. Earlier, Foxconn announced that Zhong Nanshan would be its general adviser on the epidemic.

If in previous years, Zhengzhou port area around Foxconn, should be busy. But on Feb. 24, only 24 restaurants opened in the 2,000-acre campus, which has a maximum of 300,000 employees, and 16,423 people used their lunch cards that day, the depthpaper reporter verified. All units, be advised to maintain one-meter perimeter.

But three days later, on the 27th, a foxconn production line in Zhengzhou started its night shift. Speeding up the pace of the resumption of work is thought to be an announced "spending" initiative -- Foxconn is offering recruitment agencies $5,000 to $7,500 in rebates, as well as subsidies for workers to help boost hiring. In Chongqing, the government will give recruitment agencies an extra 2,000 yuan in back fees. Recruitment conditions, there is also a "first in history" breakthrough.

But the effect still seems to be getting stronger. Taiyuan Foxconn Personnel Department staff confirmed to reporters that even if last year resigned and left, now re-entry, also can enjoy 90 days of attendance more than 6,000 yuan new entry incentive. He said that although has achieved, people, but the gap is still.

What Cui may not have realised is that this is the "hardest" and "most expensive" season for the global contract manufacturing juggernaut. In this back-to-work season, money is not even the most important issue, more important than money is time and people, and "money" can not quickly solve the "time and people" problem. Although many workers, are looking forward to returning to work, although many young people are willing to work at Foxconn.

Foxconn in Yantai, which was facing embarrassment when 80 per cent of its workers were surveyed about their willingness to return to work a year ago, is just over half so far. Under pressure from new orders from one of Japan's best known brands, a simpler and more straightforward approach has been launched -- a 'lock in' bonus for those already employed.

Overall, under a variety of incentives, the majority of new staff to come close, the number has not seen a surge in external analysis of the order default pressure, as of press time, Foxconn did not respond. But a local government official told reporters that from the staff to the situation, Foxconn can catch up with the new orders, is a challenge. It's an expensive "back to work" season

And when Foxconn faced "the most expensive" in almost all history, one of the "hardest" back-to-work seasons in China's manufacturing industry, the question is whether such an expensive return to work is affordable for all but the big manufacturers like Foxconn?

The "most expensive" return to work

In contrast to other companies, Foxconn has made clear it wants to spend money to hire. And there is plenty of variety in the forms and targets of the money. Between 2,000 yuan and 7,000 yuan, there is always one for new and old employees, or recruitment agencies.

But Choi young-keung won't get the money for a while. The veteran employee stayed at home in panic, he prepared to drive back to Zhengzhou, self-isolation at home, ready to work at any time, the end of their work history of the longest this Spring Festival holiday.

February 21, "Foxconn iDPBG Zhengzhou General Recruitment" certification official said IDPBG (integrated Digital Product Business Group)2 ~ 14 levels of employees, if the February 29 has been on duty, or before February 29, although not on duty but returned to the site, and on duty before March 18 employees, 60 days, reward 3250 yuan, 90 days, bonus 2000 yuan. It is understood that before this, the above-mentioned employees'incentive bonus for returning to work is 3000 yuan per person.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Foxconn workers eat in Zhengzhou. Isobath reporter, Jiang Zheng, photography

There are plenty of older foxconn workers in the same situation as Cui. Earlier, Zhengzhou foxconn based on the extent of the epidemic in Henan, divided into high, general, low three-level risk areas, and later the division of the region has been slightly adjusted. According to this, high-risk area employees need to provide 14-day home isolation certificate, commitment letter and health certificate, General Risk area employees need to provide commitment letter and health certificate, low-risk area to provide a commitment letter can be directly joined.

Cui Yongqiang is in a high-risk area in Henan. Health certificates and quarantine aside, the commitment letter must be signed on the inside of Foxconn APP "Ai Pocket" , the content is mainly a promise of no fever, no contact Wuhan personnel.

Yantai Foxconn is also encouraging older workers to return to work in a timely manner. The local policy is that older workers work 10 days before the end of February and are rewarded with one month's salary; those who work five to 10 days before the end of February are rewarded with half a month's salary.

For workers from different regions, Foxconn in Yantai implements different segregation policies. Workers from outside the province can only take up positions in dormitories after 14 days'isolation, while workers from inside the province can only take up positions in dormitories after 7 days'isolation, return to duty in Yantai City after 3 days'isolation. During the quarantine, wages were paid, and some workers joked that "you can make money lying down. ".

Taiyuan Foxconn IDPBG staff also confirmed that although the resumption of work has been delayed, but wages are as usual. Taiyuan Foxconn Human Resources Department staff told reporters, February 24 to March 31 during the induction of employees, 90 days of attendance can get 6250 yuan bonus. Under the policy, about 1,000 people are recruited every day, but that's not enough.

He also revealed that Taiyuan Factory area existing employees about 70,000 people, as of February 26,30,000 people have returned to work, the rest will continue to work. The reporter asks, if last year quit a job to enter a factory again this year, whether belong to new employee. He said the situation was a bonus for new employees.

But the old staff is limited, Foxconn's employment characteristics, it seems more need to recruit new to quickly realize the resumption of work. Recruitment, it is necessary to rely heavily on intermediaries.

Zhang Hua (not his real name) of a human resources company told the reporter of the CONTOUR line that Foxconn in Zhengzhou started to resume work on February 10 and started hiring on February 16. The return fee that Labor agents received from the company has already risen to 7,500 yuan, the prerequisite is that the employee will be on the job for three months.

At 25 yuan an hour, the agent takes 2 yuan and the worker gets 23 yuan an hour, which Zhang Hua says is also significantly higher than previous years. At one point, it was embarrassing that the building where Zhang Hua's company was located had been sealed off before work resumed on Feb. 10 at the request of the State Council. Today, Zhang Hua's company is only halfway back to work, and its sales staff are on the front line, but the rest of the department is just back online.

More likely, the agency has a separate agreement with Foxconn, under which both sides are more focused on the rapid growth of jobs and the relative stability of personnel.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
At 1900 hours on February 29, Foxconn employees at the Zhengzhou port area, which is located in the Zhengzhou Xinzheng Comprehensive Bonded Zone, began working the night shift. Isobath reporter, Jiang Zheng, photography

Letter Guangda Human Resources Services Co. , Ltd. in the face of the recruitment policy, Port Area FOXCONN IDPBG business group February 21 one-time rebate policy is to punch a card for 55 days, more than 90 days can get 6000 yuan rebate.

By February 28, the company's recruitment policy is divided into two models: one for employees a one-time rebate of 7,000 yuan, 35 days, and more than 60 days to pay 3,300 yuan, 55 days, and more than 90 days to pay 3,700 yuan. Mode 2 is hourly mode with a total hourly wage of $23 per hour on 7 days per month. There has been a marked increase in the amount of money being spent.

But the return fee, far from the highest, for a well-known computer manufacturer recruitment agency information, the return fee up to 15,000 yuan, and particularly stressed that workers are sitting time. And intermediary industry personage says, now higher return fee is 17,000 yuan!

A Human Resources Co. , Ltd. , a person in charge of the "depth of the line" reporter said that his region, if the Foxconn sent to Zhengzhou, the staff on duty for 90 days, 55 days, can receive a dispatch fee (repatriation)7000 Yuan. "The contribution fee varies slightly from region to region, but it is only about 200 yuan lower. Relatively speaking, the contribution fee is quite high. "

At this point, it seems to rely on the advantages of large population of the province to start to highlight. But Yantai Foxconn is not so optimistic, leaving aside the return fee to the agency, in order to encourage old employees to recommend new employees, the reward has increased from 800 yuan to 1,600 yuan, the current maximum reward is 2,200 yuan.

Similarly, Foxconn in the Zhengzhou port area has similar incentives. According to an internal foxconn document in Zhengzhou, in addition to the normal salary and overtime pay, those who return to work are entitled to an incentive payment of 60 yuan per person per day. Can Not Return to the post because of the priority can be arranged annual leave, insufficient can be arranged special leave.

At foxconn in Zhengzhou, the official number mentioned above, new employees who enter the company through self-recommendation, rehiring after leaving the company, internal recommendation and other channels will be rewarded up to 5,250 yuan as long as they meet the 90-day limit.

"Some of the agents themselves are not able to return to work completely, and relying on the agents may really be worse than relying on the old staff. If he can come back to work, he can bring people. This is a more practical approach, especially in the more rural, traditional Central Plain area. " February 29, beijing, a person in charge of human resources told the "deep line" reporter.

The person in charge further confirmed that some agents in Beijing, Guangzhou and Shenzhen received a refund of up to 17,000 yuan is real, but the rate of recruitment of new agents, and the return fee is difficult to say directly proportional. "during the Spring Festival, what you see is still a traditional, local and even conservative society. The role of intermediaries is limited, so don't overestimate it. Especially in terms of what people think about the epidemic. "

Of course, Yantai Foxconn also gives new employees 200 yuan bonus for the first month, in addition, as of the end of May this year, new employees enjoy meal compensation (12 yuan per day) .

"Most difficult" return to work

What drives up the "cost" of Foxconn's rehabilitation can be found in the simplest terms of supply and demand. According to the interviews conducted by the reporter of "The contour" in many places, it is precisely the relative shortage of labor on the job that has pushed up foxconn's "price of returning workers' human resources, " and this is related to a series of prevention and control measures since the outbreak of the new pneumonia, this includes both restrictions on labour mobility and restrictions on the ability to take on human resources hardware as a result of the requirements of operating conditions.

The reporter learned that, at least at the moment, the recruitment of thousands of people, Foxconn has been able to take out the better results. If you want more people, it's not about money, it's about time.

Zhang Qinglin (not his real name) , an employee who has joined Foxconn in Zhengzhou, told the contour that one person lived in a dormitory during the isolation period. There are no more dormitories, and employees who need isolation will not be allowed to return to work until the epidemic prevention and control policy is adjusted.

The space for epidemic prevention and control continues to be adjusted. The reporter from the "contour line" learned that with the newly adjusted regional division, the high-risk areas in Henan Province have been divided into 53 districts and counties under the jurisdiction of 16 cities and counties, including Zhengzhou (directly under the jurisdiction of the province) , adjusted to: 7 cities, counties (provinces directly under the county) under the jurisdiction of 14 districts, counties employees can not return to work.

"CONTOUR" reporters verify that on February 24, a total of 46 restaurants in the Zhengzhou port area of Foxconn, the opening of 24 restaurants, the same day lunch card 16,423 people, for the first quarantine zone personnel 6,734 people.

It should be noted that due to the special period of the restaurant dining process cumbersome, a large number of employees choose to solve their own lunch. Another person familiar with the matter revealed that Foxconn in Zhengzhou has recently recruited around 6,000 or 7,000 new workers in the area around the plant. That compares with the number of new workers at Yantai Foxconn -- as many as 1,000 a day.

On Feb. 27, Zhang Lili, who works on the plate, told the contour that on that day, Foxconn in the Zhengzhou port area started working night shifts, which can be divided into two types. One is 1930 to 0430, and if you work overtime, it's extended to 0630. The other is 2000 to 0500, if overtime, extended to 0700 am.

"actually, I came back to Yantai early, but because I had children, I had to live at work because I had to go to work, and although the incentives were great, I didn't go to work in the first place for the sake of safety and children, " said a longtime employee at Foxconn in Yantai, who did not want to be named. Suffice it to say, beyond policy, how employees actually weigh up these rewards is also an important factor.

Of course, even if you are willing to return to work, the actual situation is also a lot of restrictions. Officials in Luoyang, Yiyang County, Henan Province, said that when migrant workers returned to their posts, they were required to sit in separate seats on the bus in addition to body temperature testing and disinfection along the way, and that the occupancy rate could only be controlled within 50 percent. "One of our town buses has an emergency area in the back two rows in case anyone on the way shows any symptoms of discomfort and can be isolated for observation. "

"according to the system software developed by Foxconn in Yantai, 80 per cent or more of its employees were willing to return to their jobs a year ago, but a large proportion of them have not returned to their factories for various reasons, and there are now more than 10,000 people returning to their factories [ on February 27] , " said a local government source in Yantai, "But we recently received new orders for Electronics from a well-known brand, and if the total number of workers needed to produce under the orders [ all orders ] is more than 30,000, there is a big gap. "

Priority Strategy

At a time when human resources are expensive and can not even be fully addressed, the question of which orders to prioritize between limited labor and capacity is a choice foxconn needs to make. It is about the structure of the global contract manufacturing Juggernaut and its future.

Cui Yongqiang estimates that the number of old employees in Henan Province who are trapped at home in an epidemic area and can not return to work should be about 35 percent of the total staff. "There are about 300,000 workers at the peak in the Zhengzhou port area and at least 150,000 on average. "

The number of lunch card swipes by Foxconn in the Zhengzhou port area rose from 16,423 on February 24 to 20,800 and 23,009 on February 25 and 26, according to the contour. This figure, with the end of isolation after the return of reserve "release" , but also with the start of the machine.

Cui Yongqiang revealed that the current resumption of employees, is in accordance with the different processes on the production line. "It's like there are 50 processes, different in the order of production, going back to work in proportion to demand. But the people who are going back to work are all from non-affected areas. "

In the actual operation process, uncontrollable factor still exists. It is not uncommon for employees to be transferred after returning to work. One employee, who joined the company a month ago, was notified of a change in position after returning to work on February 25, the details of which have yet to be determined.

More human resources to the manufacturing sector. Zhang's team was assigned to support the Manufacturing and assembly of mobile phones. "Right now the staff is making the arrangements a priority, " he said.

At the same time, mobile phone manufacturing and assembly work longer hours. Zhang Qinglin told the contour reporter that the manufacturing link employees are currently working 8 hours a day, plus 3 hours of overtime, 13 days in a row can be a day off.

At present, Foxconn Technology Group in Zhengzhou has three plant areas, namely the Zhengzhou Airport Plant area, the Jingkai plant area, the Zhongmu County plant area. Foxconn is the largest in port. In 2019, Henan Province exported 218.31 billion yuan of mobile phones, the largest single export commodity in the region. Much of that is coming out of Foxconn's port area.

Cui appears confident that his company's business will be affected. He believes that even in previous years, after the Spring Festival also belongs to the low production capacity period, and there are inventories. Capacity is expanding rapidly as conditions permit. As things stand, peak capacity could easily be reached in 10 days if people were in place.

But the key is still people, especially those who are distributed in specific production links. Several workers at Foxconn in Chongqing told the contour that the factory began taking workers back to the factory in batches on February 24. However, the workers who had already returned to the factory were still at work because the workers had not arrived, but "there is nothing to do, play" .

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
FOXCONN's Chongqing plant is located in Chongqing Xiyong comprehensive bonded zone, off-duty hours, the entrance of the few people. By Cheng Wei, isobath reporter, photography

In addition to money, conditions for hiring are also being further relaxed.

In Zhang Hua's impression, the original Zhengzhou Foxconn does not open hourly workers, Zhang Hua told reporters, only began to recruit hourly workers at the end of 2019, because the end of the year is a peak production season, it was difficult to recruit people, only open hourly workers, at that time the employee hourly work 21 yuan per hour, now the hours have all gone up to $23 an hour. Zhang Hua argues that factory wages have risen in response to the epidemic, but that this is normal in special times.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
During a 20-minute aerial photograph taken after work on Feb. 25, few people and vehicles moved around the Foxconn plant in Chongqing. By Cheng Wei, isobath correspondent

Compared with Central Plain's rework drive, the Chongqing Foxconn plant, which was billed as having 60,000 employees, is small and appears to be returning to work at a more measured pace because it mainly makes laptops. On the evening of February 25, a rework worker told the contour that foxconn returned to the Chongqing Plant in stages, first picking up nearby workers and then workers relatively far away.

The Chongqing Foxconn worker said 30 workers returned to the factory on Feb. 24 and 1,300 on Feb. 25. About 11,000 workers were working in the factory before the Spring Festival. Foxconn, which started production in May 2010, has an annual capacity of 20m laptops and accessories.

"from an industrial point of view, mobile phones in the electronic age are more like consumer goods. The high demand in the market determines that the risk of default is very high. For laptops, the risk of default is much lower because of demand. If you can rank Foxconn's current level of rehabilitation, you can rest assured that it will be exactly in line with the market demand,"the head of sales line of a well-known notebook manufacturer in Beijing told the CONTOUR.".

As the world's largest contract factory, in recent years, with the increase in labor costs, contract workers have been gradually thin profit has been hon Hai Group (Foxconn parent)'s heart disease. Hon Hai also wants to turn the iPhone foundry into a diversified company, as the smartphone market continues to slow and its main business, mobile contract manufacturing, comes under pressure.

Since 2002, Hon Hai has sought to transform its business by joining IBM in environmental and cloud computing, entering the health care market, buying sharp panels and moving into the memory chip market. Still, making things for apple is a big part of the business for Foxconn, Hon Hai's subsidiary. Apple orders account for a significant portion of FIH Mobile Limited's earnings.

Guo Mingwei, an analyst with Tianfeng Securities, said that apple has cut iPhone shipments by about 10% in the first quarter of 2020 due to the outbreak. Apple will ship only 36 million to 40 million iphones in the first quarter of 2020.

Earlier reports pointed out that, "given current market conditions, sales are expected to grow by 1-3 per cent in 2020, " Liu Yangwei, foxconn chairman, said in response to questions about whether Hon Hai would cut sales this year. The figure is below its January 22 forecast of 3-5 per cent, it was also lower than the 5.4 percent average forecast by analysts.

However, in response to the information, a Foxconn source told reporters on February 5: "At present [ Hon Hai ] does not officially provide external financial figures. "

On Feb. 20, Hon Hai issued a statement saying that the company does not comment on market assessments of the Group's operations or release quarterly financial figures, according to the Taiwan Stock Exchange's website. He also said that due to the impact of the new pneumonia outbreak, the company will be more cautious in the resumption of work at major factories in mainland China under the principle that the safety of employees is the first priority and the resumption process is legal and compliant, it does have a negative impact on year-round revenue. Some overseas factories, including Vietnam, India, Mexico and other places continue to operate full load, some expansion plans are also in normal progress, the overall details will be clarified after the situation.

"please keep your distance one meter. "

At the moment, however, the No. 1 Problem Foxconn faces remains epidemic prevention. If something goes wrong, it makes the expensive ones back to work even more expensive.

According to Foxconn technology group February 25, Zhong Nanshan has served as the group's new pneumonia prevention and re-work general consultant.

It's unclear what advice Zhong Nanshan gave Foxconn. "More than a metre apart" has become a phrase that has been used with extreme frequency in and around the foxconn factories in Zhengzhou and Yantai. "Deep Line" reporters in the recruitment center to see Foxconn in Zhengzhou, the old staff in this queue for entry procedures, several employees briefly huddle to chat, was the scene of staff scolded.

In addition, the entry line, dining line, take the shuttle bus line, into the dormitory disinfection line, are required at least one meter interval. Protective goods become scarce. Zhang Qinglin told the reporter, "isodepth line" , after normal work, the factory area will give the staff a mask every day, dormitory inside also has the disinfectant.

Zhengzhou Port Area Foxconn plant area and the dormitory are not together, the larger several dormitory and the park has certain distance. There are shuttle buses to take employees directly from the factory to their dormitories. However, some staff still choose to walk back to their dormitories. There are several living areas on the way. At present, all the dormitories of Foxconn in Zhengzhou have been closed, to enter the need to hold a certificate, take body temperature and after multiple disinfection.

The epidemic prevention of the dining link is more complicated. On February 25th Wang Guosheng, the party secretary of Henan Province, paid a visit to Foxconn. The reporter of the isodesline found that the workers came out of the production workshop, walked through a corridor of about 100 meters and entered the dining area. At the entrance to the restaurant, the floor is marked with a line separating the employees from each other by more than one meter.

People familiar with the matter revealed that the current implementation of the Zhengzhou Foxconn Park staggered peak dining, not allowing employees to eat by themselves. Every 20 people form a group, the group eat together, and then leave together. Each batch of meals leave, someone will be on the table for a disinfection, and then clean with water, and then the next batch of dining staff can sit down.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Inside a Foxconn restaurant in Yantai, China

At foxconn in Yantai and Zhengzhou, new office-like baffles have been added to the dining tables.

The lives of the employees have changed a lot since they returned to work. "Deep Line" reporters on February 24,25 field visits, Zhengzhou Foxconn Park around the food and beverage are almost not open, only some supermarkets, pharmacies are open. Due to the complexity of the dining procedure in the staff dining room during the special period, employees who do not want to eat here do not have many choices, instant noodles and ham are almost standard.

There are staff introduction: "Half of our department is to eat instant noodles. ". Instant noodles, steamed buns and pickles are out of stock at Wojinhualian Supermarket, a large supermarket near the Foxconn campus in the Zhengzhou port area. Everyone says the current situation is 'Foxconn to work, master Kong to work' . "

Foxconn aside, government support is everywhere. Early praise of the "hard core" epidemic prevention in Henan, in the resumption of work, but also to give positive measures.

In the past week, Wang Honglai, deputy director of the Songxian Social Welfare Bureau in Luoyang City, coordinated seven groups of local migrant workers to return to their posts at Foxconn in Zhengzhou. "Our county had more than 5,700 workers working at Foxconn in Zhengzhou last year. The first seven batches have already arranged for more than 440 people to return to work. We expect that by the end of March, our migrant workers in Song County will be able to return to work in general. "

On February 27, he told the "contour" reporter, after communication with the port area Foxconn, through the coordination of the Zhengzhou Port Area People's Social Bureau, Foxconn arranged vehicles to go directly to the local personnel pulled away. Before returning to work, they need to issue a number of certificates for the workers.

According to incomplete statistics, Henan Puyang, Anyang, Luohe, Pingdingshan, Luoyang and other places have similar policies. On February 24, the Zhengzhou traffic police also escorted foxconn employees'free cars to the foxconn campus, local media reported.

In Chongqing, the government has also offered incentives to recruitment agencies: The local government subsidizes them by more than 2,000 yuan if they recruit a worker for Foxconn, Quanta and other factories in Chongqing. The agency did not say how much the subsidy would be. However, workers who rotate from factory to factory in the park will not be eligible for the subsidy unless they are absent from work for more than a month during the changeover.

In the interview, each park, the level personnel, reveals to the reporter returns to the post the proportion is different, but most thought at present is far lower than in the same period in previous years. A government official said privately that Foxconn had just received an order from a well-known company for game consoles, and he and his colleagues thought there must be pressure on Foxconn to supply new orders under the pressure of old ones. This judgment is based on their observation of the number of workers who have returned to work over the past few days.

Everyone is looking forward to a much better situation, so that both the resumption of work and production capacity do not seem to need so much anxiety. But this is a difficult to judge the time distance, can not be measured by the distance between employees one meter. As of press time, Foxconn headquarters and various plant areas have not accepted the "contour" reporter interview.

(editor: Hao Cheng, PROOFREAD: Yan Jingning)
